heading: Howling Warren Dungeon Guide
content: Howling Warren features the , and Werewolves. Lots of Werewolves. Overall it's a little long, but at least you won't have a boss to contend with at the end, making this one satisfying if you're target-farming the Werewolf monster family. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
